
URL Shortener
This is a simple Django application that shortens long URLs and provides redirection to the original destination.

Features:

Generates short, unique codes for long URLs.
Redirects users to the original URL when they access the shortened code.
Getting Started

Prerequisites:

Python 3.x
Django framework
Installation:

Clone this repository.
Create a virtual environment: python -m venv venv
Activate the virtual environment: source venv/bin/activate (Windows) or source venv/bin/activate.sh (Linux/macOS)
Install dependencies: pip install -r requirements.txt
Run database migrations: python manage.py migrate
Usage:

Start the development server: python manage.py runserver
Access the application in your browser: http://localhost:8000/
